| 111 |    35 | F     |
| 112 |    55 | C     |
| 113 |    65 | B     |
| 114 |    85 | A     |
| 115 |    75 | B     |
| 116 |    40 | C     |
| 117 |    90 | A     |
+-----+-------+-------+
